	 a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is no elevator. Stai
	rs only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. Arriv
	e early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When purchasing ADA 
	accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by email if assistance
	 is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us at 
	accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless free
	standing chair for patrons with mobility impairments and their companions.
	 Please note that our historic theatre has no elevator to the balcony leve
	ls. Please note\, the ADA section on the seating map does not represent a 
	specific seat location.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/black-label-societ
